hopobject.body: I can't get a dialling tone viamedic.com/msl Acer says that the C720 is 30 percent thinner than its predecessor, at three-quarters of an inch thick, and its 1,366x768-pixel, 11.6-inch screen has a new, reduced-glare matte display. It's also a quarter of a pound lighter than the C710. But the big selling point is its battery life, which Acer says ought to last up to 8.5 hours, more than double the advertised battery life of 3 hours, 50 minutes on the previous model.
